				"number": "1",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"11263\"></a>Översikt över tillgängliga 5-ASA-preparat för behandling av IBD<sup><a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_12\"><sup>a</sup></a></sup>",
				"id": "b4_20",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Substans</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Preparat</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Indikationer</strong></div></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Dosering</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Akut skov</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Underhållsterapi</strong></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Perorala beredningar</strong></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029455\" data-text=\"sulfasalazin:IBD\"></a>Sulfa-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">salazin</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029458\" data-text=\"Salazopyrin:IBD\"></a>Salazopyrin tabletter och <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Salazopyrin EN enterotabletter</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ulcerös kolit och <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Mb Crohn </div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">2 g x 3–4</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1 g x 2</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029467\" data-text=\"mesalazin\"></a>Mesalazin</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029470\" data-text=\"Pentasa\"></a>Pentasa depottabletter<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">Pentasa Sachet depotgranulat</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ulcerös kolit</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1 g x 3–4<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">2 g x 2 </div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,5–1 g x 2<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">2 g x 1</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029481\" data-text=\"Asacol\"></a>Asacol enterotabletter </div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ulcerös kolit</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,8 g x 3–4</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1,6–3,2 g x 1<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">0,4–0,8 g x 2</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Salofalk enterodepotgranulat</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ulcerös kolit</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1,5–3 g x 1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1,5 g x 1<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">500 mg x 3</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1033649\" data-text=\"Mezavant\"></a>Mezavant enterodepottablett</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ulcerös kolit</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">2,4–4,8 g x 1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">2,4 g x 1</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029490\" data-text=\"olsalazin\"></a>Olsalazin</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029493\" data-text=\"Dipentum\"></a>Dipentum kapslar och tabletter</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ulcerös kolit</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1 g x 2–3</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,5 g x 2</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029502\" data-text=\"balsalazid\"></a>Balsalazid</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1029505\" data-text=\"Colazid\"></a>Colazid kapslar</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ulcerös kolit</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">2,25 g x 3</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1,5 g x 2</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Rektala beredningar</strong></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div>